      "para_id": "Q000934.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) To Šul-šagana , the beloved child of Ninĝirsu , her master , Ninḫedu , the spouse of Nammaḫni , ruler of Lagaš , the child of Ur-Bau , ruler of Lagaš , dedicated this ( mace ) for her well-being ."
    }
  ],
